{"TopicId":182161,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"Opportunity Easter Egg on Duna, please","CreatedByName":"Mars-Bound Hokie","CreatedById":192121,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-14T05:20:13Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Mars-Bound Hokie","CreatedById":192121,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-14T05:20:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI wonder if Squad will add an easter egg for Opportunity in the next update. After all, how can we not forget that little robot who explored the Martian surface for 15 years - and when it was supposed to die after 90 days.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022SjQRzZE.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022415\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/SjQRzZE.jpg\u0022 width=\u0022601\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:26px;\u0022\u003E\u0022My battery is low and it\u0027s getting dark\u0022 (Opportunity\u0027s final words)\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\nIf anyone else would like to pay respects, visit my \u0022\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/182162-opportunity-eulogy/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EOpportunity Eulogy\u003C/a\u003E\u0022 post\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-02-14T05:26:40Z\u0022 title=\u002202/14/2019 05:26  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 14, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Mars-Bound Hokie\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealKerbal3x","CreatedById":183830,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-14T06:51:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think if they added an Easter egg, they wouldn\u2019t mention it. We\u2019d have to find it for ourselves.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, it\u2019s not really for Opportunity, but there\u2019s already a buried Curiosity chem-cam on Duna.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MaverickSawyer","CreatedById":11952,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-14T06:54:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223540464\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022182161\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221550127086\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022183830\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022RealKerbal3x\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, RealKerbal3x said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think if they added an Easter egg, they wouldn\u2019t mention it. We\u2019d have to find it for ourselves.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, it\u2019s not really for Opportunity, but there\u2019s already a buried Curiosity chem-cam on Duna.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nShouldn\u0027t be all that hard to add one at the right location, though... maybe have it do Morse code of the \u0022final words\u0022?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealKerbal3x","CreatedById":183830,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-14T07:23:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223540466\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022182161\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221550127273\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002211952\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MaverickSawyer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n28 minutes ago, MaverickSawyer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nShouldn\u0027t be all that hard to add one at the right location, though... maybe have it do Morse code of the \u0022final words\u0022?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, a morse code signal at the last known coordinates would be nice.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klgraham1013","CreatedById":105132,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-14T13:00:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI just want more rover parts....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"l0kki","CreatedById":182979,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-14T14:24:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223540548\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022182161\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221550149207\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022105132\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022klgraham1013\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, klgraham1013 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI just want more rover parts....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd i want a reason to build rovers\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klesh","CreatedById":110814,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-14T15:55:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPeople are getting way too\u00A0emotionally involved with a robot.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MaverickSawyer","CreatedById":11952,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-14T16:18:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223540604\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022182161\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221550159702\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022110814\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022klesh\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n19 minutes ago, klesh said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPeople are getting way too\u00A0emotionally involved with a robot.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHeretic! Unbeliever!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAll joking aside, it is sad to see one of missions that truly cemented my fascination with Mars finally come to an end, especially like this. I mean... Opportunity was active for nearly half my life. I think that only the ISS, Cassini, and the Voyagers have been active missions for longer.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"EchoLima","CreatedById":61992,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-14T18:17:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223540619\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022182161\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221550161109\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002211952\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MaverickSawyer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, MaverickSawyer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E think\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E that only the ISS, Cassini, and the Voyagers have been active missions for longer.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHubble too, but it was reserviced.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2001 Mars Odyssey is also older.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-02-14T18:18:47Z\u0022 title=\u002202/14/2019 06:18  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 14, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by EchoLima\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EAdded 2001 Mars Odyssey\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MaverickSawyer","CreatedById":11952,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-14T18:20:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGood points. I\u0027d forgotten about Odyssey and Hubble.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow THAT\u0027S one that will unleash a flood of tears when it falls silent...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-14T23:05:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou guys know there already sort-of is one, right? (Not my pic.)\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Jon1R.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022480\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/Jon1R.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAt any rate, this suggestion for the game\u0027s development has been moved to Suggestions \u0026amp; Development.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MaverickSawyer","CreatedById":11952,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-14T23:53:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223540878\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022182161\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221550185550\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002227914\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vanamonde\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n47 minutes ago, Vanamonde said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou guys know there already sort-of is one, right? (Not my pic.)\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/Jon1R.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Jon1R.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 height=\u0022480\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/Jon1R.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, and SQUAD put in a memorial for Neil Armstrong after he died. Having some new Easter Eggs related to spaceflight wouldn\u0027t be unwelcome. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u00A0Now, not saying that every mission that\u0027s landed on another planet should get one, but some notable missions should be honored. Opportunity certainly counts in my book.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAt any rate, this suggestion for the game\u0027s development has been moved to Suggestions \u0026amp; Development.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ZooNamedGames","CreatedById":103726,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-15T07:14:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223540878\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022182161\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221550185550\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002227914\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vanamonde\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 hours ago, Vanamonde said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou guys know there already sort-of is one, right? (Not my pic.)\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/Jon1R.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Jon1R.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 height=\u0022480\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/Jon1R.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAt any rate, this suggestion for the game\u0027s development has been moved to Suggestions \u0026amp; Development.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSomeone should check on it though. A lot of Easter eggs have become entirely inaccessible or viewable over the years and it\u2019s possible the rover may also have been lost during all the updates\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xurkitree","CreatedById":187694,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-15T11:58:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223541081\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022182161\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221550214888\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022103726\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ZooNamedGames\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, ZooNamedGames said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSomeone should check on it though. A lot of Easter eggs have become entirely inaccessible or viewable over the years and it\u2019s possible the rover may also have been lost during all the updates\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nnope, all the easter eggs have been checked to ensure they haven\u0027t sunken in or anything. Earlier versions had Easter Eggs deep underground but they have been fixed as far as I can tell.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klgraham1013","CreatedById":105132,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-15T12:28:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223540878\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022182161\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221550185550\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002227914\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vanamonde\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n13 hours ago, Vanamonde said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou guys know there already sort-of is one, right? (Not my pic.)\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI question the scale of some of the easter eggs in this game...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"EchoLima","CreatedById":61992,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-15T14:44:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223541196\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022182161\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221550233717\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022105132\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022klgraham1013\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, klgraham1013 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI question the scale of some of the easter eggs in this game...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey used to be smaller. The monolith near \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E used to be barely visible from the space center, for example.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"PunkyFickle","CreatedById":130214,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-15T19:07:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223541196\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022182161\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221550233717\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022105132\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022klgraham1013\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, klgraham1013 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI question the scale of some of the easter eggs in this game...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, according to the wiki (the biology section is particularly hilarious, btw), a Kerbal is 0,75 m tall and Curiosity is around the size of a car \u003Cspan\u003E:\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022PIA15279_3rovers-stand_D2011_1215_D521.j\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022516\u0022 src=\u0022https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/42/PIA15279_3rovers-stand_D2011_1215_D521.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWikipedia \u003Cspan\u003E:\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ci style=\u0022color:#222222;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003ECuriosity\u003C/i\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#222222;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003Ehas a mass of 899\u00A0kg (1,982\u00A0lb) including 80\u00A0kg (180\u00A0lb) of scientific instruments.\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#222222;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003EThe rover is 2.9\u00A0m (9.5\u00A0ft) long by 2.7\u00A0m (8.9\u00A0ft) wide by 2.2\u00A0m (7.2\u00A0ft) in height.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo that\u0027s actually rather close to reality \u003Cspan\u003E:\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022w8MrDCL.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022717\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/w8MrDCL.jpg\u0022 width=\u0022886\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStandard height for the other stuff measured in the picture.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-02-15T19:37:11Z\u0022 title=\u002202/15/2019 07:37  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 15, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by PunkyFickle\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klgraham1013","CreatedById":105132,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-15T19:08:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223541257\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022182161\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221550241857\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002261992\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022EchoLima\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, EchoLima said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey used to be smaller. The monolith near \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E used to be barely visible from the space center, for example.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAh, the good old days.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223541382\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022182161\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221550257676\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022130214\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022PunkyFickle\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, PunkyFickle said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo that\u0027s actually rather close to reality\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe more you know.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Duck McFuddle","CreatedById":188882,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-16T16:44:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think it would be nice to have a little easter egg for dear old Opportunity. Squad wouldn\u0027t announce it, but we would have to find it ourselves.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-16T17:09:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223541382\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022182161\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221550257676\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022130214\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022PunkyFickle\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n21 hours ago, PunkyFickle said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, according to the wiki (the biology section is particularly hilarious, btw), a Kerbal is 0,75 m tall and Curiosity is around the size of a car \u003Cspan\u003E:\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/42/PIA15279_3rovers-stand_D2011_1215_D521.jpg\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022PIA15279_3rovers-stand_D2011_1215_D521.j\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 height=\u0022516\u0022 src=\u0022https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/42/PIA15279_3rovers-stand_D2011_1215_D521.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat might just be the coolest pic I have seen of all the rovers, clearly showing the relative sizes.\u00A0 I have followed them all fairly closely, I remember watching the Sojourner landings on TV.\u00A0\u00A0 I wonder if they ever do races around the test track....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223541769\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022182161\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221550335493\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022188882\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Duck McFuddle\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n25 minutes ago, Duck McFuddle said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think it would be nice to have a little easter egg for dear old Opportunity. Squad wouldn\u0027t announce it, but we would have to find it ourselves.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust a few posts up, you\u0027ll see it\u0027s already in the game...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MiscelanousItem","CreatedById":194744,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-16T17:13:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223541784\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022182161\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221550336991\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002264714\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gargamel\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Gargamel said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust a few posts up, you\u0027ll see it\u0027s already in the game...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNope\u003Cbr\u003E\nThe Chem-cam is from Curiosity\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRIP Opportunity\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-16T17:14:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223541789\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022182161\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221550337202\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022194744\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MiscelanousItem\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, MiscelanousItem said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNope\u003Cbr\u003E\nThe Chem-cam is from Curiosity\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRIP Opportunity\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhich is true, but I would consider that an easter egg for all the rovers.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"PunkyFickle","CreatedById":130214,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-16T18:37:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223541784\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022182161\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221550336991\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002264714\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gargamel\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Gargamel said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat might just be the coolest pic I have seen of all the rovers, clearly showing the relative sizes.\u00A0 I have followed them all fairly closely, I remember watching the Sojourner landings on TV.\u00A0\u00A0 I wonder if they ever do races around the test track....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t have much credit; the picture is on the wikipedia page of Curiosity. I don\u0027t really see races being that exiting due to the difference in top speed, endurance contests, however...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rover 6428","CreatedById":184753,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-28T20:11:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif;\u0022\u003EI think that MER-1 (Oppy) should be given some credit for working for so over 15 years, and since it is now officially dead, I think it would be nice to add him into the game. Of course it doesn\u0027t have to be a statue, but maybe some other kind of easteregg.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-02-28T20:12:04Z\u0022 title=\u002202/28/2019 08:12  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 28, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Rover 6428\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Duck McFuddle","CreatedById":188882,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-28T20:33:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis has already been suggested, but only by mention in the opportunity eulogy thread. I would love it if this happened. Opportunity definitely\u00A0deserves some sort of easter egg, and KSP has commemorated things/people before (Armstrong statue on the Mun).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe do already have a little rover cam sticking out of the ground already, but that is not specifically\u00A0devoted to any one rover.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Image result for ksp rover easter egg duna\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/Jon1R.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}